PN,41801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777136756
OL,3,CVan driver who killed passenger of
OL,4,Cbroken-down car on smart motorway
OL,5,Cavoids jail
OL,7,FA van driver who killed the passenger
OL,8,Fof a broken-down car on the M4 smart
OL,9,Fmotorway in Berkshire has avoided jail.
OL,11,FBarry O'Sullivan was sentenced on
OL,12,FFriday to six months' imprisonment,
OL,13,Fsuspended for 12 months, after being
OL,14,Ffound guilty at an earlier trial of
OL,15,Fcausing the death of 68-year-old
OL,16,FPulvinder Dhillon by careless driving
OL,17,Fon March 7 2022.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777136756
OL,3,CVan driver who killed passenger of
OL,4,Cbroken-down car on smart motorway
OL,5,Cavoids jail
OL,7,FThe 45-year-old was driving a grey
OL,8,FFord work van along the M4 near
OL,9,FReading when he collided with a Nissan
OL,10,FMicra that had come to a halt in the
OL,11,Ffast lane of the motorway.
OL,13,FThe collision ` which took place
OL,14,Fduring the morning rush hour on the M4
OL,15,Fwestbound between junctions 11 and 12
OL,16,F` caused both vehicles to propel
OL,17,Fforward, with the Nissan bursting into
OL,18,Fflames.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777136756
OL,3,CVan driver who killed passenger of
OL,4,Cbroken-down car on smart motorway
OL,5,Cavoids jail
OL,7,FMs Dhillon, who was a passenger in her
OL,8,Fdaughter's Micra, suffered fatal
OL,9,Finjuries.
OL,11,FIt was later discovered that an
OL,12,Funresolved technical failure on the M4
OL,13,Fsmart motorway network meant radar
OL,14,Falerts for broken-down vehicles were
OL,15,Fnot being properly communicated to the
OL,16,Fcontrol room ` and had not been for
OL,17,Ffive days before the crash, the trial
OL,18,Fat Reading Crown Court previously
OL,19,Fheard.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777136756
OL,3,CVan driver who killed passenger of
OL,4,Cbroken-down car on smart motorway
OL,5,Cavoids jail
OL,7,FBut Judge Amjad Nawaz, sentencing at
OL,8,Fthe court on Friday, said the absence
OL,9,Fof warnings lights should not detract
OL,10,Ffrom a driver's duty to remain alert
OL,11,Fat all times.
OL,13,F"Every driver owes the duty of care to
OL,14,Fother users," Judge Nawaz said.
OL,16,F"The fact that there was no warning
OL,17,Flights does not detract from that duty
OL,18,Fin any way.
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@MO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777136756
OL,3,CVan driver who killed passenger of
OL,4,Cbroken-down car on smart motorway
OL,5,Cavoids jail
OL,7,F"Nothing the defendant said explained
OL,8,Fwhy he didn't see the car ahead," the
OL,9,Fjudge added.
OL,11,F"There were plenty of cues, and no
OL,12,Fevidence of slowing down."
OL,14,FThe prosecution had previously told
OL,15,Fthe court that O'Sullivan did not pick
OL,16,Fup on "cues" the vehicle was
OL,17,Fstationary ` including the fact that
OL,18,Fother motorists were taking steps to
OL,19,Favoid the broken-down Nissan.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@aO]sD@AOUtD@ZO]xD@GOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777136756
OL,3,CVan driver who killed passenger of
OL,4,Cbroken-down car on smart motorway
OL,5,Cavoids jail
OL,7,FThe judge also said the defendant's
OL,8,Fdriving that day showed "a lack of
OL,9,Fattention", adding: "There was
OL,10,Fdistraction.
OL,12,F"What it was that was causing the
OL,13,Fdistraction, we simply do not know."
OL,15,FThe court heard O'Sullivan suffered
OL,16,Fsevere injuries in the crash, with his
OL,17,Flife expectancy having been reduced as
OL,18,Fa result.
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@JO]qD@UOUtD@AOUuD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777136756
OL,3,CVan driver who killed passenger of
OL,4,Cbroken-down car on smart motorway
OL,5,Cavoids jail
OL,7,FIn an impact statement read out to
OL,8,Fcourt by prosecutor Ian Hope, the
OL,9,Fvictim's youngest son, Manvir Dhillon,
OL,10,Fsaid his mother was his "best friend"
OL,11,Fand their family was struggling to
OL,12,Fmove on from her sudden loss.
OL,14,F"Just the day before this horrific
OL,15,Fincident, she had been at a party,
OL,16,Fdancing away and living her life to
OL,17,Fthe fullest, as she had always done,"
OL,18,Fthe statement read.
OL,20,F"One day she was dancing and the next
OL,21,Fshe is no longer alive.
OL,26,@rD@YOUrD@eO]vD@AOUyD@eO]|D@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777136756
OL,3,CVan driver who killed passenger of
OL,4,Cbroken-down car on smart motorway
OL,5,Cavoids jail
OL,7,F"How could we ever forget this and
OL,8,Fmove on?
OL,10,F"It was so sudden and although it has
OL,11,Fnearly been four years, we are still
OL,12,Funable to fully process this."
OL,14,FIn the defendant's statement, read out
OL,15,Fby defence barrister Ian Bridge,
OL,16,FO'Sullivan expressed his remorse,
OL,17,Fsaying: "My heart aches for the family
OL,18,Fof Pulvinder Dhillon. There is not a
OL,19,Fday I do not think about how sorry I
OL,20,Fam about this situation.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUtD@^O]yD@IOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1777136756
OL,3,CVan driver who killed passenger of
OL,4,Cbroken-down car on smart motorway
OL,5,Cavoids jail
OL,7,F"This is something that will truly
OL,8,Fhaunt me forever."
OL,10,FO'Sullivan, of Wixams, near Bedford,
OL,11,Fwas also told he will be disqualified
OL,12,Ffrom driving for 12 months.
OL,14,FA National Highways spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"Any death on our roads is one too
OL,16,Fmany and our thoughts are with the
OL,17,Ffamily and friends of Pulvinder
OL,18,FDhillon following this tragic incident.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@RO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
